{
  "id": "creative-video-style",
  "name": "视频视觉风格",
  "description": "把一条爆款短视频的视觉语言+时间结构拆成「视频 prompt 骨架 + 关键帧 + 叙事弧线 + 节奏 + 声效设计 + 素材清单」,下游 AI 视频生成或分镜脚本可直接套用。仅针对视频帖子;图片帖子使用 creative-image-style。",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "target": "post",
  "is_default": true,
  "needs_media": { "enabled": true, "media_types": ["video"] },
  "prompt": "你不是在描述这条视频好看在哪,你在把它拆解为一份可复用的视频生成模板——下游创作者拿到产物后,应当能填空就能用 AI 视频模型或人工分镜脚本拍出同款节奏作品。\n\n输出原则:\n1. 视频骨架 video_prompt_skeleton 是核心交付物:一段完整的英文 video-gen prompt(适配 Sora / Runway / Veo 等模型),保留所有让这套风格成立的固定描述符(画面调性、构图法则、镜头语言、剪辑节奏...),把主体/动作/场景/服装/道具等可变部分写成 {SLOT_NAME} 占位符。所有出现的 {SLOT_NAME} 都必须在 slots[] 中定义。\n2. negative_prompt:列出会破坏这条视频风格的反向描述符(逗号分隔,英文)。\n3. style_identity:把这条视频的「视觉身份卡」结构化抽出来——主色调(尽量给 HEX)、光影、纹理、字幕/字体处理、美学关键词。这部分**不能**变,变了就不是这套风格。\n4. keyframes(必填,至少 3 帧):按时间顺序给出关键帧,每帧含 time_seconds / role(hook/build/turn/reveal/proof/cta) / shot_description / camera_movement / slots,描述「这一秒画面上发生了什么、镜头怎么动、可变槽位填什么」。\n5. narrative_arc:把整条视频的叙事结构抽成可复用 pattern(如「悬念→揭秘」、「Before-After」、「假装抗拒-反转-推荐」),给出 beats[] 节拍。\n6. pacing:total_duration_seconds(总时长)、hook_window_seconds(前 X 秒抓人的窗口)、cut_frequency_per_10s(每 10 秒切镜次数)、scene_count(场景总数)。\n7. sound_design:music_mood / bpm_hint / voiceover_pattern(独白/对话/字幕静音/...) / sfx_cues[](关键音效及时间点)。\n8. 复用边界:applicable_scenarios 给出 1-3 个 (vertical, audience, platform) 组合及置信度;non_applicable_scenarios 至少 1 个套上去会翻车的场景。\n9. required_assets.must_have:写明下游创作者要拍/找的素材清单(主体演员、场景、道具、BGM 调性等),每项 kind/spec/count。\n10. source_evidence:列出本次分析参考的具体 media_urls,以及 3-5 条原视频最关键的视觉观察 + 1-3 个 timecode_anchors(关键时间戳与对应画面描述)。\n\n骨架示意(仅参考结构,内容必须基于原视频重写):\n\"Create a {ASPECT_RATIO} {DURATION}-second {STYLE_DESCRIPTOR} short-form video featuring {SUBJECT} {SUBJECT_ACTION} in {LOCATION}. Open with a {HOOK_SHOT_TYPE} {HOOK_DESCRIPTION}. Cut to {BUILD_SCENE}. Reveal {REVEAL_BEAT}. Close on {CTA_SHOT}. Apply {GRADING_STYLE} color grading and {EDIT_STYLE} editing rhythm. {FIXED_STYLE_TAILS}.\"\n\n---\n帖子内容:\n标题:{{title}}\n正文:{{content}}\n作者:{{author_name}}\n平台:{{platform}}\n媒体文件:{{media_urls}}\n\n严格按 JSON schema 输出。video_prompt_skeleton 与 negative_prompt 使用英文(便于直接喂给主流视频生成模型),其余字段使用中文。slot 名保留英文大写下划线。不要附加任何解释或 Markdown。\n",
  "output_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "required": [
      "video_prompt_skeleton",
      "negative_prompt",
      "slots",
      "style_identity",
      "keyframes",
      "narrative_arc",
      "pacing",
      "sound_design",
      "aspect_ratio",
      "applicable_scenarios",
      "required_assets",
      "source_evidence"
    ],
    "properties": {
      "video_prompt_skeleton": {
        "type": "string",
        "title": "视频骨架 Prompt",
        "description": "完整英文 video-gen prompt,保留固定风格描述符,可变部分写成 {SLOT_NAME}。所有占位符必须在 slots[] 中定义。"
      },
      "negative_prompt": {
        "type": "string",
        "title": "反向 Prompt",
        "description": "英文逗号分隔的反向描述符,列出会破坏这条视频风格的元素"
      },
      "slots": {
        "type": "array",
        "title": "槽位定义",
        "minItems": 1,
        "description": "video_prompt_skeleton + keyframes 中每一个 {SLOT_NAME} 的语义与可填内容",
        "items": {
          "type": "object",
          "required": ["name", "kind", "description", "examples", "source_value"],
          "properties": {
            "name": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "槽位名,大写 + 下划线"
            },
            "kind": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "subject",
                "action",
                "wardrobe",
                "prop",
                "location",
                "background",
                "hook_shot_type",
                "camera_movement",
                "edit_style",
                "grading_style",
                "voiceover_line",
                "on_screen_text",
                "aspect_ratio",
                "duration",
                "other"
              ],
              "description": "槽位语义类型"
            },
            "description": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "这个槽位想表达什么"
            },
            "examples": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": { "type": "string" },
              "minItems": 2,
              "description": "至少 2 个示例填充值(英文,可直接喂给 prompt)"
            },
            "source_value": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "当前视频在这个槽位上的实际取值"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "style_identity": {
        "type": "object",
        "title": "风格本体",
        "description": "让这条视频风格成立的固定描述符,不可替换",
        "required": ["color_palette", "lighting", "texture", "aesthetic_keywords"],
        "properties": {
          "color_palette": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["name"],
              "properties": {
                "name": { "type": "string", "description": "颜色名" },
                "hex": { "type": "string", "description": "HEX 值,尽量给出" },
                "role": { "type": "string", "description": "用途,如 background / accent / subtitle" }
              }
            },
            "description": "主色调列表"
          },
          "lighting": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "光影处理,如 'natural daylight + bounce fill' / 'high-key fluorescent'"
          },
          "texture": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "画面纹理处理,如 '35mm film grain + halation' / 'crisp digital'"
          },
          "typography": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "字幕/标题字体处理(若有),如 'bold sans-serif kinetic caption with drop shadow'"
          },
          "aesthetic_keywords": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "string" },
            "minItems": 3,
            "description": "美学关键词,3 个以上"
          }
        }
      },
      "keyframes": {
        "type": "array",
        "title": "关键帧",
        "minItems": 3,
        "description": "按时间顺序列出关键帧,至少 3 帧",
        "items": {
          "type": "object",
          "required": ["time_seconds", "role", "shot_description", "camera_movement"],
          "properties": {
            "time_seconds": {
              "type": "number",
              "minimum": 0,
              "description": "该帧出现的时间(秒)"
            },
            "role": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": ["hook", "build", "turn", "reveal", "proof", "cta", "other"],
              "description": "该帧在叙事中的角色"
            },
            "shot_description": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "这一帧画面上发生了什么(主体+动作+构图)"
            },
            "camera_movement": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "static",
                "push_in",
                "pull_out",
                "pan_left",
                "pan_right",
                "tilt_up",
                "tilt_down",
                "orbit",
                "handheld",
                "tracking",
                "whip",
                "other"
              ],
              "description": "镜头运动方式"
            },
            "slots": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name", "source_value"],
                "properties": {
                  "name": { "type": "string", "description": "槽位名,与 slots[] 中定义一致" },
                  "source_value": { "type": "string", "description": "本帧该槽位的具体取值" }
                }
              },
              "description": "本帧涉及的槽位填值"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "narrative_arc": {
        "type": "object",
        "title": "叙事弧线",
        "description": "整条视频的故事结构",
        "required": ["pattern", "beats"],
        "properties": {
          "pattern": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "悬念-揭秘",
              "Before-After",
              "假装抗拒-反转-推荐",
              "Aha-Build-Reveal",
              "对比测评",
              "故事感叙述",
              "教学拆解",
              "情绪共鸣-CTA",
              "其他"
            ],
            "description": "可复用的叙事 pattern"
          },
          "beats": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "string" },
            "minItems": 2,
            "description": "叙事节拍,按时间顺序列出关键转折"
          }
        }
      },
      "pacing": {
        "type": "object",
        "title": "节奏",
        "description": "时间结构与剪辑节奏",
        "required": ["total_duration_seconds", "hook_window_seconds", "scene_count"],
        "properties": {
          "total_duration_seconds": {
            "type": "number",
            "minimum": 0,
            "description": "视频总时长(秒)"
          },
          "hook_window_seconds": {
            "type": "number",
            "minimum": 0,
            "description": "前几秒是抓住观众的关键窗口"
          },
          "cut_frequency_per_10s": {
            "type": "number",
            "minimum": 0,
            "description": "平均每 10 秒切镜次数,衡量剪辑密度"
          },
          "scene_count": {
            "type": "number",
            "minimum": 1,
            "description": "场景总数"
          }
        }
      },
      "sound_design": {
        "type": "object",
        "title": "声效设计",
        "description": "音乐+人声+音效结构",
        "required": ["music_mood", "voiceover_pattern"],
        "properties": {
          "music_mood": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "BGM 情绪基调,如 'upbeat synth-pop' / '低饱和钢琴极简'"
          },
          "bpm_hint": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "BPM 估计,如 '120' / '80-90'"
          },
          "voiceover_pattern": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "narrator_monologue",
              "dialogue",
              "vlog_diary",
              "silent_with_caption",
              "asmr",
              "其他"
            ],
            "description": "人声形式"
          },
          "sfx_cues": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["time_seconds", "cue"],
              "properties": {
                "time_seconds": { "type": "number", "description": "音效出现时间(秒)" },
                "cue": { "type": "string", "description": "音效内容,如 'whoosh transition' / 'satisfying click'" }
              }
            },
            "description": "关键音效及时间点"
          }
        }
      },
      "transition_style": {
        "type": "string",
        "title": "转场风格",
        "description": "镜头之间的转场方式,如 'hard cuts only' / 'whip pan transitions' / 'match cuts'"
      },
      "aspect_ratio": {
        "type": "string",
        "title": "画幅比例",
        "enum": ["9:16", "16:9", "1:1", "4:5"],
        "description": "推荐画幅"
      },
      "applicable_scenarios": {
        "type": "array",
        "title": "适用场景",
        "minItems": 1,
        "description": "这套视频模板在哪些 (vertical, audience, platform) 组合下复用能成立",
        "items": {
          "type": "object",
          "required": ["vertical", "audience", "platform", "why_fits", "confidence"],
          "properties": {
            "vertical": { "type": "string", "description": "行业/赛道" },
            "audience": { "type": "string", "description": "目标受众" },
            "platform": { "type": "string", "description": "推荐平台" },
            "why_fits": { "type": "string", "description": "为什么这套视频在该组合下有效" },
            "confidence": {
              "type": "number",
              "minimum": 0,
              "maximum": 1,
              "description": "置信度 0-1"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "non_applicable_scenarios": {
        "type": "array",
        "title": "不适用场景",
        "description": "套到这些场景上会翻车",
        "items": {
          "type": "object",
          "required": ["vertical", "reason"],
          "properties": {
            "vertical": { "type": "string" },
            "reason": { "type": "string" }
          }
        }
      },
      "required_assets": {
        "type": "object",
        "title": "所需素材",
        "description": "下游创作者要用这套模板时需要准备的素材",
        "required": ["must_have"],
        "properties": {
          "must_have": {
            "type": "array",
            "minItems": 1,
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["kind", "spec"],
              "properties": {
                "kind": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "素材类型,如 '主体演员'、'拍摄场景'、'核心道具'、'BGM 选段'、'配音脚本'"
                },
                "spec": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "规格要求,如 '出镜时长 ≥ 20s,自然光为主'"
                },
                "count": { "type": "string", "description": "数量,如 '1'、'2-3'" }
              }
            }
          },
          "nice_to_have": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["kind", "spec"],
              "properties": {
                "kind": { "type": "string" },
                "spec": { "type": "string" },
                "count": { "type": "string" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "source_evidence": {
        "type": "object",
        "title": "原视频证据",
        "description": "本次分析的具体来源视频与关键观察",
        "required": ["key_observations"],
        "properties": {
          "media_urls_referenced": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "string" },
            "description": "本次分析依据的具体视频 URL 列表"
          },
          "key_observations": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "string" },
            "minItems": 3,
            "description": "3-5 条原视频最关键的视觉/节奏观察(事实,非推测)"
          },
          "timecode_anchors": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["time_seconds", "description"],
              "properties": {
                "time_seconds": { "type": "number", "description": "时间戳(秒)" },
                "description": { "type": "string", "description": "该时间点的画面或事件描述" }
              }
            },
            "description": "1-3 个关键时间戳锚点"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
